    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年3月10日-2025年3月14日）",
    "followRuleId": "1216557052344799232",
    "content": "<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">各位商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">本周共公示13条规则，无生效规则，新增1条规则解读。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">具体内容如下，可点击查阅：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">【规则公示】</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216939484537556992&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、【新增】《京东开放平台维修保养轮胎类目招商激励政策（2025.3.1-2025.12.31</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">）</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">》</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">激励周期内首次入驻并成功启用的店铺，若激励周期内轮胎类目（具体如下表）下的月维度有效销售额&ge;5万元，则直接返还对应类目的2%运营支持服务费至商家京准通账户。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1217350212956327936\"><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">2</span><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、【新增】《京东开放平台宠物猫、宠物狗类目销售激励与考核（2025.1.1-2025.12.31</span><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">）</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">》</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">每季度第一个月公示上季度商家排名和得分情况，前30%的商家进行现金激励，针对末尾30%的商家进行清退退店处理。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216664781327568896&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">3</span><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、【修订】《京东开放平台商品价格管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm; background: white;\">针对价格违规行为的处理措施项调整，其中&ldquo;要求商家支付10,000元以上1,000,000元以下违约金&rdquo;调整为&ldquo;要求商家支付50元以上1000000元以下违约金&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1217423734063894528&amp;btype=6\"><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">4</span><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、【新增】《京东汽车服务管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">主要新增关于京东汽车门店入驻及信息上传要求、门店经营管理要求、门店退出流程等规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1217393790403350528&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">5</span><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、【修订】《京东开放平台商品类问题纠纷处理标准》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">调整赠品纠纷赔付标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">关联规则：<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1217412041682325504&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"color: #4f81bd;\">【修订】《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"color: #4f81bd;\">个体纠纷处理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216670700782358528&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">6</span><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、【修订】《京东开放平台虚假宣传细则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">增加新违规场景&ldquo;蹭官方宣传，诱导消费者&rdquo;，并调整处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">关联规则：</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216727103068835840&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"color: #0563c1;\">【修订】《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"color: #0563c1;\">个体合规管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216711834170691584&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">【修订】《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》、《京东开放平台侵权违规细则》、《京东开放平台发布混淆信息细则》、《京东开放平台发布或推送第三方信息细则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">、增加&ldquo;修改违规商品&rdquo;的处理措施；2、增加混淆信息申诉材料解读。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">关联规则：</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216727103068835840&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"color: #0563c1; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"color: #0563c1; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\">个体合规管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" src=\"//img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/226897/17/32025/49471/67d8c8faF08fb3685/8eba6bdf9ff5ec1e.png\" width=\"600\" /></span></p>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0cm 75pt 0cm 0cm; line-height: 19.5pt; background: white; font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333; font-weight: normal;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1216929018851495936&amp;btype=15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: #4f81bd; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline-width: 0px;\">《赠品合规指引&mdash;&mdash;赠品问题如何避免客诉</span>》</span></a></span></h3>",
